tasks.description:
Write the SQL migration files for the multi-tenant schema restructuring.

Read docs/platform-architecture.md (from T1) and GarudaX_Strategy_Directive.md §3.2 and §5.
Read infrastructure/db/migrations/V1__core_schemas.sql for existing schema names.
Read .softhouse/handoff/T1.md for the architecture decisions.

Create two migration files:

**infrastructure/db/migrations/V29__platform_schemas.sql:**
- CREATE SCHEMA platform;
- CREATE TABLE platform.tenants (id VARCHAR(64) PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL, status VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'ONBOARDING' CHECK (status IN ('ACTIVE','SUSPENDED','ONBOARDING','DECOMMISSIONED')), flagship BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE, governance_tier VARCHAR(20) DEFAULT 'STANDARD', onboarding_metadata JSONB DEFAULT '{}', created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT NOW(), updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT NOW());
- INSERT INTO platform.tenants (id, name, status, flagship) VALUES ('ace-commodities', 'ACE Commodity Exchange', 'ACTIVE', false), ('mse-equities', 'Mongolian Stock Exchange', 'ONBOARDING', true);
- CREATE TABLE platform.audit (id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(), tenant_id VARCHAR(64) REFERENCES platform.tenants(id), event_type VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL, actor VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL, details JSONB NOT NULL DEFAULT '{}', created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT NOW());
- Indexes on tenants(status), audit(tenant_id, created_at)
- GRANT statements for platform service role

**infrastructure/db/migrations/V30__ace_schema_renames.sql:**
- ALTER SCHEMA reference RENAME TO ace_reference;
- ALTER SCHEMA participants RENAME TO ace_participants;
- ALTER SCHEMA exchange RENAME TO ace_exchange;
- ALTER SCHEMA clearing RENAME TO ace_clearing;
- ALTER SCHEMA compliance RENAME TO ace_compliance;
- ALTER SCHEMA warehouse RENAME TO ace_warehouse;
- ALTER SCHEMA market_data RENAME TO ace_market_data;
- ALTER SCHEMA securities RENAME TO ace_securities;
- auth stays as-is (platform-level per directive §3.4)
- Add comments explaining the rename for each schema
- Note: application code must be updated in a subsequent migration to reference new schema names

Follow existing migration conventions (check V25 or V26 for style).

Write handoff to .softhouse/handoff/T2.md
